      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Aug 22 obituary of the theater director Michael Maggio</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary of the theater director Michael Maggio on Tuesday misstated the title of the last play he directed. It was ''Boy Gets Girl'' by Rebecca Gilman, not ''Boy Meets Girl.''</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An obituary of the theater director Michael Maggio on Tuesday misstated the title of the last play he directed. It was ''Boy Gets Girl'' by Rebecca Gilman, not ''Boy Meets Girl.''</p>
